SPARE
COPIES.
To
d. no: 51
No. 75/CF/52
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA
CABINET SECRETARIAT
New Delhi, the 22nd May, 1957.
....
The undersigned is directed to inform Members of
the Council of Ministers that Shri Kotha Raghuramaiah
assumed office as Deputy Minister with effect from the
foreroon of 21st May, 1957. He will be attached to the
Ministry of Defence.
- 107
Rumeshchandra
(Ramesh Chandra)
for Secretary to the Cabinet.
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
...
Copy forwarded to the Deputy Chairman, Planning Commission,
for information.
KOHLI
300 copies.
Copy forwarded to the Secretary to the President/the
Private Secretary to the Vice-President/the Special Assistant
to the Prime Minister/the Principal Private Secretary to the
Prime Minister, for information.
Rameshchandon
(Ramesh Chandra)
Under Secretary to the Cabinet.
Copy forwarded to all Secretaries to the Government of
India/Chairman, Railway Board/Joint Secretary, Planning
Commission, for information.
Copy forwarded to all Ministries of the Government of
India (including Ministry of Railways)/Department of
Parliamentary Affairs/Planning Commission/Department of
Atomic Energy/Prime Minister's Secretariat/Lok Sabha Secretariat/
Rajya Sabha Secretariat, for information.
Rameshband.
(Ramesh Chandra)
Under Secretary to the Cabinet.
Copy to:-
Military Wing/Establishment Section/Administration Section/
O & M Division.
